Module hu.unipannon.virt.plot
Package hu.unipannon.virt.plot.data

Class BarData

  • java.lang.Object
    • hu.unipannon.virt.plot.data.BarData
  • public class BarData
extends java.lang.Object
    Data class to store a series of data for a bar plot. Only contains Y coordinates (values), these data points will be colored the same on the graphical representation of the plot.
    Author:
    Tóth Bálint
